### Cloud Testing for Microsoft Expert Agent
### Deployed to Azure Functions
### BASE_URL and FUNCTION_KEY loaded from .env (gitignored)

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}
@functionKey = {{$dotenv FUNCTION_KEY}}

### ============================================
### CHAT ENDPOINT
### ============================================

### Chat - Foundry question
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat?code={{functionKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "What's the difference between classic and new foundry?"
}

### Chat - Azure pricing question (session auto-captured)
# @name pricingChat
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat?code={{functionKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "What is the price of a Standard D4s v5 VM in East US?"
}

### Chat - Azure cost calculation
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat?code={{functionKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "If I run 10 million executions per month of Azure Functions, what would that cost annually?"
}

### ============================================
### MULTI-TURN CONVERSATION
### ============================================
### session_id is captured automatically from the pricingChat response above
### Run the pricingChat request first, then run this one

@sessionId = {{pricingChat.response.body.$.session_id}}

### Follow-up in the same session (no manual copy-paste needed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat?code={{functionKey}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-ms-session-id: {{sessionId}}

{
    "prompt": "If I run that VM 24/7 for a month, what would it cost?"
}
